77c3a554724e51ee7131f62c83a","tid":1607991,"uid":164374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T06:36:56.000Z","msg":"年紀咁大..."},{"pid":"9ac901d53d6e2419e357c8e772a6eab1231b8ec5","tid":1607991,"uid":2429,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T06:40:13.000Z","msg":"仲有撚江派咩，一早收編晒。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e7ff0b8d97fd3020a8f532cf8c8e356b9abf8567","tid":1607991,"uid":149494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T06:40:25.000Z","msg":"佢就黎頂唔住架啦<br />\n要靠手足們你地幫佢手反習啦"},{"pid":"235a27debd7ece3dfb57e9a10b164766c643a1f0","tid":1607991,"uid":271434,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T06:49:03.000Z","msg":"<strong>我以颱風風眼橫過比喻，預測閱兵期間香港唔會發生衝突</strong><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">昨日警察不斷恐嚇大家十一唔好出，同埋有很多假消息話各地暴徒會燒商場，呢個奇怪現象同早幾日批不反對通知書後立即大搜捕完全不同，<span style=\"color: red;\">就係因為警察知道，十一當日唔可以捉人、唔可以出現血腥畫面，</span><span style=\"color: gold;\">但中共又唔容許有大量人上街反共反雜，所以先嚇定大家。<br />\n</span><br />\n現在就好似颱風風眼即將略過時候，警察瘋狂捉人，製造白色恐怖。<span style=\"color: red;\">風眼將會在閱兵期間橫過香港，忽然晴天萬里，到時候社會上一定太平無事，警察唔會拉人，大家可以放膽出街。</span><span style=\"color: blue;\">但要小心，當10月1日半夜過後，就有可能好似風眼過後，又出現狂風暴雨，</span>所以大家意見表達完結後，就盡快返歸，唔好戀戰。<br />\n<br />\n點解警察聽日閱兵期間唔捉人？<span style=\"color: gold;\">因為北大人唔想在世界各地直播閱兵期間，同時直播出現血腥鎮壓嘅場面，咁會落佢面，令雜種即時受到黨內外以及西方社會譴責，</span>所以十一閱兵嘅時候唔會清場鎮壓。<br />\n<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">聽講呢個安排僅十一閱兵嘅時段限定！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1606271\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1606271</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n今日香港慘劇係雜種一手造成，冤有頭債有主，請大家對準政權目標<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">有明確訊息證實係習近平一人當日堅持拒絕「撤回」及下令將44人極速起訴暴動！</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1602129\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1602129</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">十一遊行要高叫「天滅中共！習近平全家死」口號落中共面！</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1568634\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1568634</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"d80c3ab863a6c4a2b45f3dabb5da14b09fb27843","tid":1607991,"uid":123848,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T07:00:27.000Z","msg":"江派睇黎大勢已去<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"42362e9df7393955eab43317f709ce7056905070","tid":1607991,"uid":262690,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T07:10:51.000Z","msg":"大佬成93 歲..."},{"pid":"b991d265f6a75208124b8a3ad3ee70e2d39803e8","tid":1607991,"uid":48796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T07:15:04.000Z","msg":"行到重想點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"26b6ba7c7017909592db81be3164678788b7e9fd","tid":1607991,"uid":265112,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T07:16:50.000Z","msg":"上次已經係"},{"pid":"fe48bc2c41658e9b204546abd987685415403d46","tid":1607991,"uid":290118,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T07:21:27.000Z","msg":"機械人嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"130c986f4dd603cc7e284ceeef80b536417f7b15","tid":1607991,"uid":135957,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T13:53:03.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a483bfc890f1830d2439a9520d4da5b21df9b473","tid":1607991,"uid":313615,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T05:15:05.000Z","msg":"有個103歲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"30e66eb8f2182fb0d3e573154857f7df9bcd3ddc","tid":1607991,"uid":135957,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T05:12:35.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"eedfdd5aeab31357fac92cd4ac9783393cc3633e","tid":1607991,"uid":41658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"130c986f4dd603cc7e284ceeef80b536417f7b15","tid":1607991,"uid":135957,"like":0,"d